snippet.title: MegaWorld Express - Compete Delivery Orders
snippet.description: In MegaWorld's autonomus cities, building owners offer MEGA rewards for completing daily delivery tasks, that help to boost production results in their buildings. Explore the orders on your phone, venture to different Districts on the gaming map and look for better rewards. Accumulate MEGA, enhance your Avatar, and even start your own production in MegaWorld.
